      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration lovers! This vehicle is the perfect 'diamond in the rough' project car for anyone looking to roll up their sleeves. While it currently needs some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back to its former glory, it offers a fantastic foundation at an unbeatable price point. Grab this opportunity to breathe new life into a classic project!",
