      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a significant project or a donor car. The exterior exhibits extensive rust on the body panels, noticeable dents, and failing paint, while the interior shows heavy wear including torn seats and broken trim pieces. Mechanically, the car requires immediate attention due to engine leaks and a worn suspension system; while it starts, it is not currently reliable for daily use without major repairs.",
