    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I'm parting ways with my car, and it's honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved and maintained. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this beauty is ready to go! Come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself. I'd love to find it a great new home! \u2728",
      "price": 32500.0,
