      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a linear power band that screams to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock, ensuring exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis remains taut with precise turn-in, and the critical subframe mounting points have been inspected for integrity. Recent service includes a VANOS system check and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the valvetrain operates with factory-spec precision. While showing minor signs of road use, this example is mechanically robust, offering the visceral, analog feedback that defines the peak of the M-division's naturally aspirated era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
