    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This meticulously cared-for vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, with only minor road peppering consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is free of tears, and all electronics, from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system, function flawlessly. Mechanically, it is sound, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced strictly on schedule. While it shows the gentle character of a pre-loved car, its structural integrity and mechanical health are superb. Includes a full set of service records and two sets of keys. A turn-key opportunity for a discerning driver who values both quality and value.",
